To write a simple Dart program to understand the language basics. 
a) Create a program that asks the user to enter their name and their age. Print out a message that tells how 
many years they have to be 100 years old. 
  
Program: 
import 'dart:io'; 
 
void main() {     
    stdout.write("What's your name? "); 
    String? name = stdin.readLineSync(); 
 
    print("Hi, $name! What is your age?"); 
    int age = int.parse(stdin.readLineSync() ?? '0'); 
 
    int yearsToHunderd = 100 - age; 
    print("$name, You have $yearsToHunderd years to be 100"); 
} 
