c) Create a program that asks the user for a number and then prints out a list of all the divisors of that 
number. 
 
Program: 
 
import 'dart:io'; 
 
void main() { 
  stdout.write("Please choose a number: "); 
  int number = int.parse(stdin.readLineSync() ?? '0'); 
  for (var i = 1; i <= number; i++) { 
    if (number % i == 0) { 
      print(i); 
    } 
  } 
} 
 
